text: Bernard Reynès (born October 18. 1953 in Meknes, Morocco) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Bouches-du-Rhône department, and is a member of the Republicans. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:People from Meknes Category:Rally for the Republic politicians Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:The Republicans (France) politicians Category:The Popular Right Category:Deputies of the 15th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
